Home Stats

Status: Closed

MLS#: 1000034212

Type: Residential - Condo

HOA/Condo Fee: $298 Monthly

Subdivision: Delaire Landing

County: PHILADELPHIA

Nice clean Condominium featuring spacious living room with sliding glass doors to outdoor 17 X 5 covered balcony, main bedroom with 3 piece ceramic tile bath and walk in closet, one additional bedroom. Modern eat-in kitchen with dishwasher, garbage disposal and refrigerator. Combo utility/laundry room. Additional storage room in hallway. Association fee includes 24/7 gatehouse security, basic Comcast TV, water and sewer, snow and trash removal, recreation center with lots of social events, two outdoor pools, observation deck over looking the Delaware river, shuttle bus service to and from Torresdale Train Station during weekday rush hours and weekly trips to super market and area shopping malls. Heating and air conditioning units replaced 11/1/2010.
